cd ~
git clone https://github.com/CounterpartyXCP/counterparty-core.git
git pull
mkdir -p ~/.local/share/counterparty-docker-data
cd ~/counterparty-core

修改全节点端口号，默认是8332，如果已经被使用了，就得修改成其他的：
vi  docker-compose.yml

安装docker
sudo apt update
sudo apt install docker.io
sudo systemctl start docker
sudo systemctl enable docker
sudo curl -L "https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/latest/download/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)" -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose
sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose
启动服务
docker-compose --profile mainnet up -d

查看三个服务运行情况
docker-compose --profile mainnet logs --tail=10 -f bitcoind 
docker-compose --profile mainnet logs --tail=10 -f addrindexrs
docker-compose --profile mainnet logs --tail=10 -f counterparty-core
 
